lenders.occupational_info: I start businesses, get them running, and either sell them or make them self sustaining

lenders.name: David
lenders.loan_because: I know what it is like to need.  I am doing well now, so I want to give the opportunity for others to succeed.
lenders.occupational_info: I work in a large hospital in the emergency department.  I take care of the sick and injured.

lenders.name: Alex
lenders.loan_because: If $25 that I would waste on something trivial can go to better use, then I'd much rather help make a difference than spoil myself.
lenders.occupational_info: I give cash loans against jewelry so people can have some cash to take care of what they need and buy their jewelry back at a later date.
